WEBVTT

00:07.880 --> 00:10.235
So what happened to him?
-He passed out.

00:10.320 --> 00:12.390
Any idea why?
-No.

00:13.280 --> 00:14.349
Sir?

00:14.840 --> 00:17.195
Well, his eyes are open.
He's conscious.

00:18.680 --> 00:20.398
Why is there a turkey
beside his head?

00:20.480 --> 00:22.914
I didn't have any frozen peas.

00:23.000 --> 00:26.117
You know, to use as a cold compress.
He bumped his head when he fell.

00:26.200 --> 00:27.758
Right, okay.

00:28.840 --> 00:31.115
Yes, that is a nasty bump.

00:34.760 --> 00:38.309
You lying, cheating, cheap bastard!

00:42.080 --> 00:45.516
Did you throw that turkey at
your husband's head, ma'am?

00:48.040 --> 00:49.393
It's organic.

00:56.520 --> 00:59.080
Come on, Toby.
-No, Oz, I got plans.

00:59.720 --> 01:02.678
I think after a myocardial
infarction, a slipped disc,

01:02.760 --> 01:05.479
and a frozen turkey attack, you'd at
least let me take you out for a beer.

01:05.560 --> 01:07.676
I promised Liv dinner and a movie.
-What movie?

01:07.760 --> 01:09.637
The one you're not going to.
-Wrap it up, boys.

01:09.720 --> 01:11.676
You guys are heading back out.
-Pardon me, sir?

01:11.760 --> 01:14.752
Number 22 has a 10-7 in Scarborough.
Tow truck rear-ended.

01:14.840 --> 01:16.671
Heaton and Mohan.
-How are they?

01:16.760 --> 01:18.318
Well, they're a lot happier
now that they know that

01:18.400 --> 01:20.356
you two are pulling a double
till they're up and running.

01:20.440 --> 01:22.715
Can't do it, sir.
-Yes, you can.

01:22.800 --> 01:24.677
Sir, Toby and I have
previous engagements tonight.

01:24.760 --> 01:27.354
Previous engagements? Not any more.

01:27.440 --> 01:30.989
Sir, you can't just put us on a double.
We do have a union.

01:31.920 --> 01:35.754
Protects us in these cases.
There's grievances we can file.

01:37.880 --> 01:40.872
Yeah, I don't think Ryder
appreciated that union threat.

01:40.960 --> 01:43.076
No, he did not.
-It was a nice try, though.

01:43.160 --> 01:44.479
Oh, thank you.

01:46.440 --> 01:49.034
Well, we got a fall. Possible
head injury at Dundas and Cox.

01:49.120 --> 01:51.031
All right.
-Here we go.

